source: crates/biome_formatter_test/src/snapshot_builder.rs
info: scss/at-rule/include-own-line-comments.scss
---

# Input

```scss
@include own-line-comments(
1px,
/* between positional args */
2px,
/* before keyword */
$very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-long-arg:10,
// before final positional
2px 4px 6px
/* before close */
);

@include own-line-comments(
$alpha:1px,
/* before keyword */
$beta:2px,
// between keyword args
$very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-long-arg1:2px,
/* before closing positional */
3px
);

```


# Formatted

```scss
@include own-line-comments(
	1px,
	/* between positional args */ 2px,
	/* before keyword */
	$very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-long-arg:
		10,
	// before final positional
	2px 4px 6px /* before close */
);

@include own-line-comments(
	$alpha: 1px,
	/* before keyword */ $beta: 2px,
	// between keyword args
	$very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-long-arg1:
		2px,
	/* before closing positional */ 3px
);

```

# Lines exceeding max width of 80 characters
```
    5: 	$very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-long-arg:
   15: 	$very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-long-arg1:
```
